                Get Windows Azure for Free</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="margin: 6px;">
            <div>
                <div>
                    <p>
                        <strong>If you are an MSDN subscriber</strong>:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Sign up for free Windows Azure subscription from the <a href="http://www.microsoft.com/click/services/Redirect2.ashx?CR_CC=200087171"
                            target="_blank">Azure MSDN subscriber benefits page</a>.</li>
                        <li>Watch the video <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GxWr1L44T9g" target="_blank">
                            Activate your MSDN Azure benefits </a>for a step-by-step process of activation.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        <strong>If you are not an MSDN subscriber, no problem!</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>You can get a Windows&nbsp;Azure 3-month free trial&nbsp;to help you get started
                            with a no strings attached subscription. Read more details on the free trial at
                            <a href="http://www.microsoft.com/click/services/Redirect2.ashx?CR_CC=200085749"
